         </ol>
      
      <h3>Takeaways</h3>
      
      <ul class="content-list">
        <li>Load your main CSS file Asynchronously</li>
        
       <li>Use priority hints to prioritise resources</li>
        
        <li>Use inline SVG to display vector elements</li>
        
        <li>Use Squoosh.app to compress your images <em>(e.g. use AVIF or WEBP)</em></li>
        
        <li>Lazy load non-critical images <em>(below the fold)</em></li>

        <li>Add <span class="code">decoding="async"</span> to non-critical images with lazy load</li>
        
        <li>Optimise your responsive images for performance</li>
        
        <li>Optimise font loading</li>
      
        <li>Follow best-practices to load your fonts</li>
        
        <li>Avoid layout shift by applying <span class="code">width</span> and <span class="code">height</span> attributes on these images</li>

        <li>Did we eliminate render-blocking scripts?</li>

      </ul>
      
